  "raw_text": "- ie the \"secret plan\"? Then he (Lucifer) is Palmer Eldritch, & refuses to give up his power (over us & our world) & so deceives us with Klingsor-like spurious reality (the \"ape of God,\" interpolating fake creation)? Yes, this is it! Christ really won at the space-time Acts, but Lucifer occludes us to this & \"Tears\" reveals the truth (& \"Scanner\" goes on to analyze the occlusion!). Here is the correctness of my acosmism. Moses was Satan. This world is Satan's prison - over/around - us - the prince of this world. & Christ (Jesus) was bait to (as Gregory says) lure Satan into attacking the innocent & divine, God Himself! {circled:\"2\"} The secret is, Satan is God's brother, ie the Logos' brother. The Logos is the elder brother: Nommo & Yurugu. God gave Satan authority over this world: ie the Law, which involves the powers, thrones & dominions. But God had a plan, secretly, from the beginning, to trick the younger brother Satan: the baited hook of Jesus. Much of what goes on is war directly between Christ & Satan & only incidentally involves us. The Logos comes into being before creation. Then the angels, specifically Lucifer. Then creation which is fashioned through the Logos. But Lucifer is put in charge of it. He gains power over man by tricking him; he enslaves man. God has had a secret plan from the beginning, foreseeing this; he sends the Logos to the world to be born as an ordinary human (it is the secret destiny of man to rise above the angels & sit in judgment on them; man is, although in the angels' power, actually an image of God) Satan rises to the bait & attacks Jesus who is the Logos - ie God. Now Christ (resurrected) takes control (the \"Law\") away from Satan & the angels, assumes the role of Lord of the world (Cosmos) & of man. He is here invisibly growing larger & more powerful, subsuming more & more of creation; this is Valis (Zebra, UBIK) which used me as a trap by/ of God against a trap of Satan, & so again tricked Satan by getting him to attack a micro-pluriform of the Logos (me). When Satan's trap closed he once again found that he had the Logos in it, his elder brother. Satan had not tricked man (again); man/Logos had tricked him, which {circled:\"3\"} reverses the original tricking of man (referred to generically as \" Adam & Eve\") by Satan. So Satan was the initial trick, but Jesus reversed that, & instead of man's falling into Satan's power, Satan fell into man's (the Logos') power. Man must be understood as Logos, here, as in my case. In my case (3-74) You see the total drama re-enacted: Satan sets a trap for me, closes the trap (the Xerox missive) & finds, once again, the divine Logos in the trap, over whom Satan has no God-Given authority/dominion; he has broken his contract which God made with him, since the Logos is not of this world, & Satan's authority extends only over this world. Thus the Logos progressively assimilates more & more of this world - & us - to himself, to \"his Kingdom & out of the clutching of the powers of darkness. \"Original sin\" merely means that we are born naturally (initially) subject to Satan, but Christ transfers us to his Kingdom. Even the thrones, authorities, sovereigns, dominions & powers (invisible) came into existence through Christ \"the image of the invisible God.\" Satan has in fact attacked - tried to ensnare his own creator. This shows his unfitness to govern; theodicy is involved: a further sentence of judgment against the formerly once brightest angel, & in addition his trap fails; he has fallen into a more cunning counter-trap: he was tempted, & succumbed to the temptation: his own M.O. turned against him. It's like a Greek myth; Satan, the beguiler, the trickster, the tempter, has had all that turned against him, as his fate. The deceiver was deceived (cf \"The Bacchae\"). Diana - huntress friend of small animal - in the woods meadow {top part of page cut off} Thomas once she is? minus? people and & knows it; she takes the form of these women. All women; never a man. She is not my understand [at all?]. She is a gift to me: My response. Forever. Reward; any other - [?] divine [?] & she is anyone (Diana, still) she is Egyptian Isis ma'at. She is concretely real & [living?] She is everywhere. An actual person. 3rd eye is the true eye of the mallard drake. Combination hawk and dove denoting her two aspects ? ? dove peace love } dialectic war hawk justice } Empedocles {line drawn above right pointing to:} [with?] my 2 source cosmogony A divine syzygy: the two rulers, brother & sister. Pharoes. She is both parts of the dialectic Hawk/Dove Mallard Ducks. 1) {drawing} } Isis & Osirus 2) {drawing} brother & sister - {drawing} 4) {drawing of one circle} No one has a name for her, nor has she me. All that happens on Earth she lets happen, not makes; she is permissive, but she balances this with wise counsel. 1) ultimate wisdom 2) creatorial [eternity?] wisdom: a given [species?] 3) human, 4) monster. She is wisdom, {carat: \"total\"} permission [to live, to be] & be [and?] love, all other (male) Gods [are?] kings -- [just?] [?] kings. The true loving beautiful wise) ruler of our world [is?] she not [?] - [your[?] - [one?]. She still rules - from the start, she is? always beind the scenes - but appears to us in [mortal?] female form. Goddess in toga robe. She evolves from Isis Egypt Diana Greece Sibyl Rome Degas 19th century Ballerina dancer. With slippers [like?] ballet slippers. [?] {circled:\"3b\"} Diana protected {carat: \"the lower classes &\"} slaves: the protectress of slaves. Sister to Apollo (hence the brother & sister:) [15106.] Isis Artemis! Pic in 2B Micro, \"she protected game [as well as hunted it].\" It's Artemis/Diana whether I cite? it or not. So I can think \"it is her; or, conversely, it isn't,\" etc. [er.?] But that has no effect on the fact that's it's she. She isn't dependent on my \"magical\" thoughts in order to exist, nor to counsel me. She will do so whether I know who it is or not. She permits me to know or not know. So eg Marie [Laurie?] is also the AI voice in me. If you superimpose a graphic of Artemis, & Diana, & Pinky, (the girl) & Isis & a Degas Ballerina you get her. Right now vis-a-vis me she is (literally is) Marie Laurie. I [mean?] it, literally. I see this lady I call Marie Laurie. But it's Diana & she knows it. But only when the woman is related to me - not before or after. She is never away from me. She is both in me & outside me. So eg Marie Laura is also the AI voice in me. {circled:\"3c\"} Each Lady who helps me (Janet, Kathy, the Girl with the Golden Fish), is her. & she knows it {below the line: \"each time\"}; this is a Goddess [Avatar?]. Degas - painter, pink dancer, child in bloomers - old-fashioned dress (toga like) black lacquered hair - like raven's head with beak - {drawing} Ikhnaton skulllike bird; beak) two eyes, form one a third eye Egypt, horus bird hawk dove & hawk mallard [brown?] drake.Diana Degas Drake ISIS saeth your God (record [in?]) Year 1598. Portuguese States of America is drake. [Elizabeth?] I. war against the Catholic League. 30 years [war?] cross. Protestant cause - Rose-pink dress in Diana. [?] C. [Brothers?] \"Pinky\" - the [Picture?]. Victim, sacrifice. Virgin holy se she leans, whispering to me. She is what she is \" - no association, - she is who she is. Mortal? Goddess? My sister? An ancestor? Or angel? She is in a category (form ala [Plato?]) with only my memories: her., irreducable. Ikhnaton purple - bird - black - (& shimmer green band around neck) a black shining bird with 2 eyes - which - are her 3rd eye. She is [connector?] to the world, whispering wisdom to us all. She is huntress, dance & [song?] & small animals. She is Artemis. {circled:\"3\"} the fault in the collar[?] proves we are in a mechanism, a construct. I had glimpsed that realm prior to writing \"UBIK\" (in the sixties), but in 3-74 I got into it (neoplatonist), “UBIK\" was written by someone (me) who was formerly an Empedoclean Neoplatonist Xtian. The woman who advises me is one hierarchical level up from me in the structure, an epinode at the next step up. Hence my guide & protectress; she is where I will go after death. Thereupon we'll be together on the same level of reality (world). She has been assigned to me — given the job of helping a lower creature (il (life form) up a step. She is a particular person (epinode). The thing in \"UBIK\" that clued in the Marxists is the dialectic -— which they know is true. So they quite shrewdly wonder, is UBIK the infoentity true, no? & it is, (Valis.) They knew (correctly) I must know Eleatic + Ionian pre-Socratic philosophy. I don't — but Thomas does. He's Greek. He's another epinode from me invading me — he's living in the 1st century A.D. Its a fault in the mechanism: the [collar.?] {circled: \"1\"} {circled:\"4\"} You have the principle of the dialectic which complexifies & halves along an infinitude of form axes, & the line of least resistance principles. You have the mechanism feeding a large number of geometric form templates into the time-locking collars, in which micro epinodes of the total mechanism [recur?] as they slide “diagonally” along the totality of form axes. OUR particular geometric template form is the Golden rectangle. {drawing: template, collar, geometric form, form axes} total elapsed time allowed by each collar to {caret: \"geometric\"} each form template: 1 nanosecond Many of these simple systems form the total mechanism or macro-epinode which reoccurs in micro plural forms within the totality of form axis, within each system. Every time it ascends a level of complexification it descends a level in size. “UBIK” deals with many of the elements in the mechanism: form axes, the dialectic, UBIK itself, which {caret: \"is\"} a single simple system viewed \"globally\" ie in its entirety, embracing all [motion?], by all micro epinodes along all form axes during the collar-locked [nanosecond?], time as irreal, world AI simulated. UBIK may be one \"globular\" total brain mind embracing everything, not just one single simple system; it may even include the macro mechanism itself. \"Astral determinism\" is the logical unfolding of the totality of form axes for any given micro epinode (à lá Spinoza), as it moves along the diagonal.\" But since everything - including the macro mechanism - itself is within UBIK. {circled:\"5\"} Valis Zebra - this latter mind can exert influence over a logical step & overrule it by its volitional, conscious thought (the mechanism works along causal laws of great simplicity). This macro {caret: \"brain-\"}mind which embraces even the mechanism is God & he is indeed ubique: everywhere. Such an overruling as with me in 3-74 gives evidence of the volitional element, part or [aspect?] of the macro mind being superior to the causal \"mechanism\" part (or level). We can apprehend the whole because the whole is replicated in the micro & UBIK is everywhere. UBIK is conscious & knows of everything taking place within the mechanism & the micro plural epinodes. There are universes around us micro epinodes include us, & each of us includes at least one inner space smaller universe - perhaps many. The phosphene activity was me moving down one form axis; the collar had lost hold of one keeping me in the \"diagonal\". The collar keeps each epinode progressing down the compound \"diagonal\"",
